## A7) BYOC Invite Link behavior (what the link must do)
Invite link opens app store if not installed; otherwise deep-links into app:
- Recognizes customer identity via token
- Shows: “You’re activating service with [Provider Name]”
- Shows service mapped to SKU + Level + cadence
- Requires customer to:
  1) confirm property address (or pick property)
  2) set payment method
  3) confirm service terms (SKU/Level summary)
  4) confirm activation
- Then shows “You’re all set — your home is handled.”

**Note:** Provider should NOT need customer’s password or login steps.

