# PART B — In-App Provider Pitch Pages (Opportunity Banners)

## B1) Opportunity screen structure (all variants)
Each variant uses the same structure:
- Headline: “Good news…”
- Subheader: zone/category context
- 4 benefit bullets (dense routes, less admin, more monthly income, BYOC)
- Founding Partner badge + scarcity (if applicable)
- CTA: Apply Now

---

